  "prompt": "Where can you find some build examples for Titan Quest?",
  "response": "If you're looking for build examples for *Titan Quest*, there are several resources where you can find detailed guides, builds, and strategies. Here are some of the best places to look:\n\n### 1. **Official Forums**\n   - The official *Titan Quest* forums hosted by **THQ Nordic** or **Iron Lore** often have dedicated sections for builds and strategies. Players frequently share their builds and discuss optimization.\n   - [Titan Quest Forums](https://steamcommunity.com/app/475150/discussions/)\n\n### 2. **Reddit**\n   - The **r/TitanQuestAE** subreddit is an active community where players share builds, tips, and advice. You can find a variety of builds for different masteries and playstyles.\n   - [r/TitanQuestAE](https://www.reddit.com/r/TitanQuestAE/)\n\n### 3. **Steam Community Guides**\n   - Steam has a wealth of user-generated guides for *Titan Quest*. You can find builds for both the base game and the *Anniversary Edition*.\n   - [Titan Quest Steam Guides](https://steamcommunity.com/app/475150/guides/)\n\n### 4. **Crate Entertainment Community**\n   - **Crate Entertainment**, the developers of *Grim Dawn*, took over support for *Titan Quest*. Their forums and Discord server often have *Titan Quest* build discussions.\n   - [Crate Entertainment Forums](https://forums.crateentertainment.com/)\n\n### 5. **YouTube**\n   - Many *Titan Quest* players and content creators share build guides on YouTube. Searching for \u201cTitan Quest builds\u201d or specific mastery combinations will yield plenty of results.\n\n### 6. **GameFAQs**\n   - GameFAQs has guides and builds submitted by players over the years. While some may be older, they can still be useful for the base game.\n   - [Titan Quest GameFAQs](https://gamefaqs.gamespot.com/pc/930985-titan-quest/faqs)\n\n### 7. **Titan Quest Wiki**\n   - The *Titan Quest Wiki* provides detailed information about skills, items, and mechanics, which can help you create your own builds.\n   - [Titan Quest Wiki](https://titanquestfans.fandom.com/wiki/Titan_Quest_Wiki)\n\n### 8. **Discord Communities**\n   - There are active Discord servers dedicated to *Titan Quest* where players discuss builds and strategies. You can find invites to these servers through the subreddit or forums.\n\n### Tips for Finding Builds:\n- Specify the version you\u2019re playing (e.g., *Anniversary Edition*, *Ragnar\u00f6k*, or *Atlantis*).\n- Mention your preferred playstyle (e.g., melee, ranged, caster) or masteries.\n- Look for builds that include itemization and skill progression.\n\nHappy hunting, and enjoy *Titan Quest*!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
